{"tid":2400432,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"塔門d牛牛好慘","createTime":"2021-02-09T02:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T16:06:59.000Z","uid":255286,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca24e4921002809e8efa2909d73df4a15acff22","tid":2400432,"uid":255286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T02:58:48.000Z","msg":"日日都好多人入塔門玩，相信都有部分人係有公德心，執走自己垃圾亦唔會騷擾野生動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有d自私撚完全唔識同動物共處，破壞牛牛屋企仲攻擊佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9OUw7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9OUw7C.jpg&h=76499253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CK-iC1XnNmv/?igshid=13b2lfb1po1op\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCK-iC1XnNmv%2F%3Figshid%3D13b2lfb1po1op&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMPY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=a21449bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCK-iC1XnNmv%2F%3Figshid%3D13b2lfb1po1op&h=c381153a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CK-iC1XnNmv/?igshid=13b2lfb1po1op</a><br />\n<br />\n再講 不斷有人踐踏草地 會破壞土壤同植物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宜家既塔門 大嶼山都好荒蕪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />牛牛仲冇糧食到要靠義工送草入島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明白宜家封9晒冇地方去 但去大自然地方大家應該尊重原生動物  唔好特登損壞植物  而巴絲去郊外見到d冇愛心既人麻煩話下佢地喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63eec77eb788246f5438625245d0a986fb959b67","tid":2400432,"uid":255286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T03:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi